    <h2 class="ui header"> Overview
      <a id="lo3-overview" class="anchor"></a></h2>
    <div class="ui content"><p>The event was not a success as some of the vital resources could not be secured. The universities cameras and media students to film the event. Although I manged to secure contact details of producers and recording engineers who attend the host university and secured their interest no one could identify any film and media students. My own financial situation also had a negative effect on the event, mid way through term I could no longer afford my own travel requirements which made organizing the event impractical. The promotional strategy in the original plan was adopted by the host artist and tested to have limited success receiving under a thousand on you tube. In hindsight I working with a group instead of on my own would be more practical. </p></div>
  </div>
</div> 

<div class="ui teal piled segment">
  <div class="active content">
    <h2 class="ui header">Budgetary considerations.
      <a id="lo3-budget" class="anchor"></a></h2>
    <div class="ui content"><p>As mentioned earlier I had finical difficulties that impeded my ability to travel through and organize/host the event. Although it would have cost only a few hundred pound in total this was money that was unavailable at the time.</p><p>This resulted in no private(personal) or public finances being available at the time (including payday loans) which virtually nullified any potential progress</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ui teal piled segment">
